<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ACTION REQUIRED: Remove Item from Physical Store</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #d9534f; /* Red for alert */
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        strong {
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h3>ðŸ”´ ACTION REQUIRED: Item Sold on <%= platformName %> - Remove from Physical Store Stock</h3>
        <p>An item was sold on an external platform and must be physically removed from inventory to prevent overselling.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Platform:</strong> <%= platformName %></li>
            <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> #<%= orderNumber %></li>
            <li><strong>SKU:</strong> <%= sku %></li>
            <li><strong>Product Title:</strong> <%= title %></li>
            <li><strong>Color:</strong> <%= color %></li>
            <li><strong>Size:</strong> <%= size %></li>
            <li><strong>Quantity Sold:</strong> <%= quantitySold %></li>
            <li><strong>Remaining Stock:</strong> <%= remainingStock %></li>
            <li><strong>Item Location:</strong> <%= itemLocation %></li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Please locate this item immediately and move it to the 'Sold/Shipped' area.</strong> The system has automatically started updating inventory on all other connected channels.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated alert. Do not reply.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Brands Discounts. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
